## Recommended Workflow

### 1. Understand current state first

```
dashboard_state  ‚Üí  see all apps, their statuses, active overrides
screenshot       ‚Üí  confirm the visible UI
```

### 2. Set up overrides for local development

```
override_app { action: "set", appName: "@cnic/main", url: "http://localhost:9100/app.js" }
```

After setting an override, the extension panel will auto-sync within ~3 seconds.

### 3. Verify changes are effective

```
dashboard_state  ‚Üí  confirm overrideUrl shows your localhost URL
screenshot       ‚Üí  confirm the UI reflects your local code
```

### 4. Make code changes, then verify

```
ensure_fresh_render  ‚Üí  reload with fresh cache after code changes
dashboard_state      ‚Üí  re-confirm state
screenshot           ‚Üí  visual check
```

### 5. Cleanup when done

```
override_app { action: "remove", appName: "@cnic/main" }
   ‚Äî or ‚Äî
override_app { action: "reset_all" }    ‚Üê removes ALL overrides at once
```

